{"tid":2316269,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"香港自由及選擇法案 H.R. 8428","createTime":"2020-12-07T18:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T04:45:15.000Z","uid":375020,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"702e4bf94e445fd8df27b6bf898bb9a55b82ecc6","tid":2316269,"uid":375020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:30:18.000Z","msg":"美國國會眾議院預料當地星期一，全體表決《香港人民自由與選擇法案》，若果獲通過，將送往參議院表決。<br />\n<br />\n由於法案被列為擱置辯論，即是不存在爭議，獲得最少三分二議員支持，立法過程進入快速通道，在全院的審議辯論限時40分鐘，不會有新的修正案。<br />\n<br />\n根據法案內容，美國政府會為已持有簽證並在美國，但返回香港後可能面臨政治迫害的港人，提供臨時保護身份，法案亦會加速處理為逃離政治迫害的香港居民赴美難民申請程序，並將這類申請，排除在美國每年整體難民接收人數限制以外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201206/IQNSHRWHPBAX3A3OWWCJB6YSCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201206%2FIQNSHRWHPBAX3A3OWWCJB6YSCI%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7LyGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=2c3a57ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201206%2FIQNSHRWHPBAX3A3OWWCJB6YSCI%2F&h=e83850e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201206/IQNSHRWHPBAX3A3OWWCJB6YSCI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563843-20201206.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563843-20201206.htm&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7LyGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=69d5f4b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563843-20201206.htm&h=17de79c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563843-20201206.htm</a>"},{"pid":"67a303013aaad216e837043259671e868031d278","tid":2316269,"uid":375020,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"702e4bf94e445fd8df27b6bf898bb9a55b82ecc6","tid":2316269,"uid":375020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:30:18.000Z","msg":"美國國會眾議院預料當地星期一，